==English==

==== Noun ====

The '''Necronomicon''', in its most common usage, was a fictional [[spell book]] created by the novelist H.P. Lovecraft.  

==Etymology==

Nekros (corpse), nomos (law), eikon (image): "An image of the law of the dead." (Possible, not verified)

==== Pronunciation ====

Necro-nomi-con